  "body": "Fix Envoy route config name for Prometheus metrics\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\nNeed to move route config name as part of Prometheus metrics label, so that:\r\n\r\n1. Prometheus fails to scrap data because of format incompatibility. Having \"-\" in the tag value causes the failure.\r\n\r\n$ cat test.txt\r\nenvoy_http_rds_test-ing-route-config_update_rejected{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\"ingress_http\"} 0\r\nenvoy_http_rds_test-ing-route-config_update_failure{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\"ingress_http\"} 0\r\nenvoy_http_rds_test-ing-route-config_config_reload{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\"ingress_http\"} 2\r\nenvoy_http_rds_test-ing-route-config_update_success{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\"ingress_http\"} 15379\r\nenvoy_http_rds_test-ing-route-config_update_empty{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\"ingress_http\"} 0\r\nenvoy_http_rds_test-ing-route-config_update_attempt{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\"ingress_http\"} 15379\r\nenvoy_http_rds_test-ing-route-config_version{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\"ingress_http\"} 13237225503670494420\r\n\r\n$ cat test.txt | promtool check metrics\r\nerror while linting: text format parsing error in line 1: expected float as value, got \"-ing-route-config_update_rejected{envoy_http_conn_manager_prefix=\\\"ingress_http\\\"}\"\r\n\r\n\r\nRisk Level: Low\r\n",
